{
  "texts": [
    "It is written in basic English, making it suitable for younger kids, tweens, or even teens who read at a lower grade level.",
    "The simplified version still functions as an online encyclopedia, but its sentences are shorter and grammar is easier to understand.",
    "Simple Wikipedia can also prove beneficial for individuals from cultures that are in the process of learning English or those with a limited understanding of the language.",
    "Additionally, it is a helpful resource for readers with learning disabilities.",
    "The genres or topics covered on Simple Wikipedia are similar to those on regular Wikipedia and include Science, History, Geography, Biographies, Mathematics, Technology, Arts and Culture, Health and Medicine, Animals and Nature, Sports, etc."
  ]
}